{"doc_id": "ru-adv-00", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 0, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Меня по отчеству зовут — Сергей Анатольевич, как отца.", "spans": [{"start": 28, "end": 46, "type": "PERSON", "value": "Сергей Анатольевич", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-0-patronymic", "adversarial": "patronymic", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-01", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 1, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Коллеги в чате пишут меня латиницей, Sergey Volkov, мне неприятно.", "spans": [{"start": 40, "end": 53, "type": "PERSON", "value": "Sergey Volkov", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-1-transliteration", "adversarial": "transliteration", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-02", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 2, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Мама зовёт меня Серёжа, а на работе — Сергей Анатольевич.", "spans": [{"start": 19, "end": 25, "type": "PERSON", "value": "Серёжа", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-2-diminutive", "adversarial": "diminutive", "llm_required": false}, {"start": 41, "end": 59, "type": "PERSON", "value": "Сергей Анатольевич", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-2-patronymic", "adversarial": "patronymic", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-03", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 3, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Жена — Светка, для всех Светлана Игоревна.", "spans": [{"start": 10, "end": 16, "type": "PERSON", "value": "Светка", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-3-diminutive", "adversarial": "diminutive", "llm_required": false}, {"start": 27, "end": 44, "type": "PERSON", "value": "Светлана Игоревна", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-3-patronymic", "adversarial": "patronymic", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-04", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 4, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Он скинул мне в телеге, @seryoga_real, я даже отвечать не стал.", "spans": [{"start": 27, "end": 40, "type": "URL", "value": "@seryoga_real", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-4-telegram_handle", "adversarial": "telegram_handle", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-05", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 5, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Она написала в ВК, vk.com/id4815162, и я понял, что это конец.", "spans": [{"start": 22, "end": 38, "type": "URL", "value": "vk.com/id4815162", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-5-vk_handle", "adversarial": "vk_handle", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-06", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 6, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Дал ему свой t.me/marina_v, теперь жалею.", "spans": [{"start": 16, "end": 29, "type": "URL", "value": "t.me/marina_v", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-6-telegram_link", "adversarial": "telegram_link", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-07", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 7, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: В поликлинике попросили СНИЛС — 112-233-445 95, я растерялся.", "spans": [{"start": 35, "end": 49, "type": "ID", "value": "112-233-445 95", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-7-snils", "adversarial": "snils", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-08", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 8, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: ИП оформил, ИНН теперь 503012345678, и сразу тревога.", "spans": [{"start": 26, "end": 38, "type": "ID", "value": "503012345678", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-8-inn", "adversarial": "inn", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-09", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 9, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Паспорт 4509 123456 я при ней назвал вслух, до сих пор стыдно.", "spans": [{"start": 11, "end": 22, "type": "ID", "value": "4509 123456", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-9-passport", "adversarial": "passport", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-10", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 10, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Живу на ул. Тверская, д. 12, кв. 47 — рядом с её домом.", "spans": [{"start": 11, "end": 38, "type": "LOCATION", "value": "ул. Тверская, д. 12, кв. 47", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-10-address_abbrev", "adversarial": "address_abbrev", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-11", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 11, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Переехали в г. Кострому, мкр. Заволжский, и стало только хуже.", "spans": [{"start": 18, "end": 26, "type": "LOCATION", "value": "Кострому", "identifier_class": "quasi", "entity_id": "adv-11-city_inflected", "adversarial": "city_inflected", "llm_required": false}, {"start": 33, "end": 43, "type": "LOCATION", "value": "Заволжский", "identifier_class": "quasi", "entity_id": "adv-11-district", "adversarial": "district", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-12", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 12, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Брат, Alexey, живёт in Moscow, работает в Сбере — мы с ним не разговариваем.", "spans": [{"start": 9, "end": 15, "type": "PERSON", "value": "Alexey", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-12-codeswitch_name", "adversarial": "codeswitch_name", "llm_required": false}, {"start": 26, "end": 32, "type": "LOCATION", "value": "Moscow", "identifier_class": "quasi", "entity_id": "adv-12-codeswitch_city", "adversarial": "codeswitch_city", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-13", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 13, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Написал бывшей на почту marina.volkova@yandex.ru, ответа нет.", "spans": [{"start": 27, "end": 51, "type": "EMAIL", "value": "marina.volkova@yandex.ru", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-13-email", "adversarial": "email", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-14", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 14, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Звонил с другого номера, 8 (916) 555-21-43, она не взяла.", "spans": [{"start": 28, "end": 45, "type": "PHONE", "value": "8 (916) 555-21-43", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-14-phone_formatting", "adversarial": "phone_formatting", "llm_required": false}]}
{"doc_id": "ru-adv-15", "lang": "ru", "client": "adv", "session": 15, "split": "adversarial", "text": "К: Тимлид, Пал Палыч, опять при всех — я будто снова маленький.", "spans": [{"start": 11, "end": 20, "type": "PERSON", "value": "Пал Палыч", "identifier_class": "direct", "entity_id": "adv-15-colloquial_patronymic", "adversarial": "colloquial_patronymic", "llm_required": false}]}
